  .mainIntroduction
    %h2.mainIntroduction__subtitle
      FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
    %ul
      %li.mainIntroduction__list
        .mainIntroduction__list__pict
          %span.mainIntroduction__list__pict__number 1
          = image_tag "pict-reason-01.jpg", alt: "pict-reason-01"
        %h3.mainIntroduction__list__text
          %span 3分
          ですぐに出品
        .mainIntroduction__list__description
          スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
      %li.mainIntroduction__list
        .mainIntroduction__list__pict
          %span.mainIntroduction__list__pict__number 2
          = image_tag "pict-reason-02.jpg", alt: "pict-reason-02"
        %h3.mainIntroduction__list__text
          %span シンプル
          で使いやすい
        .mainIntroduction__list__description
          めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
      %li.mainIntroduction__list
        .mainIntroduction__list__pict
          %span.mainIntroduction__list__pict__number 3
          = image_tag "pict-reason-03.jpg", alt: "pict-reason-03"
        %h3.mainIntroduction__list__text
          手数料
          %span 業界最安
        .mainIntroduction__list__description
          最大3%でお得に出品&購入！
  .mainMiddleVisual
    .mainMiddleVisual__box
      %h2.mainMiddleVisual__box__subtitle
        会員数日本一位
      %p.mainMiddleVisual__box__text 
        FURIMAは、フリマアプリで最も人気。
        %br
